 to be sexy, but there was a way for Givenchy and LVMH to explain why they =
switched out this specific ingredient without scaring people or using the c=
lean beauty rhetoric that has started to fall out of favor. That communicat=
ion problem is a pervasive challenge for companies across Big Beauty. <br/>=
 <br/><i>Lauren</i>: So what has happened in the past five years with respe=
ct to =E2=80=9Cclean beauty=E2=80=9D? How has that discourse changed? <br/>=
<br/><i>Rachel</i>: It=E2=80=99s the same as any other fad, just like when =
