=99t all that healthy, either. <i>Clean</i> beauty is similar, and the tren=
d has also been normalized by the industry to the point
where it isn=E2=80=99t much of a differentiator. I=E2=80=99ve heard that Se=
phora is quietly moving away from <i>Clean at Sephora</i>, which is a big d=
