 true that Fenty has been its only star=E2=80=94were it not for Fenty=E2=80=
=99s success, Kendo would be irrelevant and might not even exist. Kat Von D=
 was a huge mess, and Marc Jacobs ceased operations a few years ago, though=
 it=E2=80=99s exciting that it=E2=80=99s coming back under new ownership wi=
